    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all 5 operating points. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
